Privacy Policy
Introduction
Welcome to our fruit cut game. Your privacy is important to us, and we are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data, and outlines your rights regarding this information.

Information We Collect
Personal Information: When you register or interact with our game, we may collect personal information such as your username, email address, and any other details you provide.
Gameplay Data: We collect data related to your interactions with the game, including scores, achievements, and gameplay preferences.
Device Information: We may collect information about the device you use to access the game, such as your device ID, operating system, and IP address.
How We Use Your Information
To Provide and Improve the Game: We use the collected data to enhance your gaming experience, including personalizing content and features.
To Communicate with You: We may use your contact information to send you updates, promotions, and other communications related to the game.
For Analytics and Research: We analyze gameplay and device data to understand user behavior and improve the gameâ€™s functionality and user experience.
Data Retention and Deletion
Retention Period: We retain your personal information and gameplay data for a maximum of 90 days after your last interaction with the game.
Automatic Deletion: After 90 days of inactivity, all your data will be automatically deleted from our servers.
User-Initiated Deletion: As data is automatically deleted after 90 days, there is no need for manual deletion requests. However, if you have specific concerns, please contact our support team.
Sharing Your Information
Third-Party Services: We do not share your personal information with third parties except as necessary to operate the game (e.g., cloud storage providers) and only under strict confidentiality agreements.
Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required by law or to protect our rights and comply with legal processes.
Your Rights
Access and Update: You have the right to access and update your personal information. Please contact our support team for assistance.
Data Deletion: While data is automatically deleted after 90 days, you can contact us if you have any concerns about your data.
Security
We implement robust security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, and destruction. Our automatic deletion process is designed to ensure that your data is not retained longer than necessary.

Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we will notify you of significant changes through the game or via email.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at shiv.sh.9867@gmail.com.

Effective Date
This Privacy Policy is effective as of 5/24/2024.

By using our fruit cut game, you agree to the collection and use of your information as described in this Privacy Policy. Thank you for playing!
